<li><cite id="CITEREFWilsonDalton1982" class="citation book">Wilson, A.J.; Dalton, D. (1982). <i>The States of South Asia: Problems of National Integration. Essays in Honour of W.H. Morris-Jones</i>. University of Hawaii Press. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-0-8248-1183-9" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-8248-1183-9">978-0-8248-1183-9</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+States+of+South+Asia%3A+Problems+of+National+Integration.+Essays+in+Honour+of+W.H.+Morris-Jones&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Hawaii+Press&amp;rft.date=1982&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-8248-1183-9&amp;rft.aulast=Wilson&amp;rft.aufirst=A.J.&amp;rft.au=Dalton%2C+D.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABengali+language" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt975" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}'/></li>
<li><cite class="citation book">Bonazzi, E (2008). <i>Grammatica Bengali</i>. Bologna: Libreria Bonomo Editrice. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-88-6071-017-8" title="Special:BookSources/978-88-6071-017-8">978-88-6071-017-8</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Grammatica+Bengali&amp;rft.place=Bologna&amp;rft.pub=Libreria+Bonomo+Editrice&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft.isbn=978-88-6071-017-8&amp;rft.aulast=Bonazzi&amp;rft.aufirst=E&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABengali+language" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt977" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}'/></li>
